00:55:45.000 --> 00:55:55.000
<c.transcription>[JIUTAI] Uchi kasanetaru tsuchi no hibiki</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] The blows coming, one on another, the sound of their mallets)</c>

242
00:55:55.000 --> 00:56:10.000
<c.transcription>Tenchi ni kikoete obitatashiya.</c>
<c.translation>(echoes throughout heaven and earth - How it resounds!)</c>

243
00:56:11.000 --> 00:56:17.000
<c.transcription>[WAKI] Kakute mitsurugi wo uchitatematsuri.</c>
<c.translation>([WAKI] And so the Imperial Blade is forged:)</c>

244
00:56:17.000 --> 00:56:22.000
<c.transcription>Omote ni Kokaji Munechika to utsu</c>
<c.translation>(On the face of it I strike: "Munechika, Swordsmith"!)</c>

245
00:56:22.000 --> 00:56:29.000
<c.transcription>[SHITE] Shintai toki no deshi nareba.</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] As your timely apprentice the god:)</c>

246
00:56:29.000 --> 00:56:39.000
<c.transcription>Kogitsune to ura ni azayakani.</c>
<c.translation>("Little Fox", I skillfully strike on the reverse.)</c>

247
00:56:40.000 --> 00:56:50.000
<c.transcription>[JIUTAI] Uchi-tatemōsu mitsurugi no</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] Along the edge of the blade are beaten traces)</c>

248
00:56:50.000 --> 00:57:00.000
<c.transcription>yaiba wa kumo wo midashitareba</c>
<c.translation>(like wild clustering clouds.)</c>

249
00:57:00.000 --> 00:57:12.000
<c.transcription>Ama-no-mura-kumo tomo kore nare ya.</c>
<c.translation>("Clustering Clouds of Heaven", it will be!)</c>

250
00:57:12.000 --> 00:57:23.000
<c.transcription>[SHITE] Ten-ga dai-ichi no.</c>
<c.translation>([SHITE] First under Heaven:)</c>

251
00:57:23.000 --> 00:57:29.000
<c.transcription>[JIUTAI] Ten-ga dai-ichi no,</c>
<c.translation>([JIUTAI] First under Heaven:)</c>

252
00:57:29.000 --> 00:57:36.000
<c.transcription>futatsu no mei no mitsurugi nite.</c>
<c.translation>(The sword with two inscriptions!)</c>

253
00:57:36.000 --> 00:57:43.000
<c.transcription>shi-kai wo osame tamaeba,</c>
<c.translation>(It will rule the land to the four seas,)</c>

254
00:57:43.000 --> 00:57:49.000
<c.transcription>go-koku jōju mo kono toki nare ya.</c>
<c.translation>(celebrate the abundance of the five staple crops.)</c>

255
00:57:49.000 --> 00:57:55.000
<c.transcription>Sunawachi nanji ga uji no shin</c>
<c.translation>("I, before you, as the deity of your clan:)</c>

256
00:57:55.000 --> 00:58:02.000
<c.transcription>Inari no shintai Kogitsune-maru wo,</c>
<c.translation>(the manifestation of Inari: the Little Fox,)</c>

257
00:58:02.000 --> 00:58:08.000
<c.transcription>chokushi ni sasage-mōshi.</c>
<c.translation>(come to aid you in fulfilling your task.)</c>

258
00:58:08.000 --> 00:58:13.000
<c.transcription>Kore made nari to ii-sutete,</c>
<c.translation>(Now, I am done!" So saying, takes his leave.)</c>

259
00:58:13.000 --> 00:58:18.000
<c.transcription>Mata mura-kumo ni tobi-nori,</c>
<c.translation>(Once more he leaps upon the mass of clouds,)</c>

260
00:58:18.000 --> 00:58:25.000
<c.transcription>mata mura-kumo ni tobi-norite,</c>
<c.translation>(Again, more he leaps upon the mass of clouds,)</c>

261
00:58:25.000 --> 00:58:52.000
<c.transcription>Higashiyama Inari no mine ni zo kaerikeru.</c>
<c.translation>(and return to Higashiyama, the eastern mountains, the peak of Mt. Inari!)</c>